<div class="editsection" style="float: right; margin-left: 5px;">[<a href="http://wiki.ubuntu.org.tw/index.php?title=Ubuntu6.06Guidetw&amp;action=edit&amp;section=262" title="Ubuntu6.06Guidetw">編輯</a>]</div><a name=".E5.A6.82.E4.BD.95.E6.89.8B.E5.8B.95.E6.9B.B4.E6.96.B0.E7.97.85.E6.AF.92.E7.A2.BC.E8.B3.87.E6.96.99.3F"></a><h5> 如何手動更新病毒碼資料? </h5>
